&lt;p>Checkout &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/content-management/page-bundles/#headless-bundle">Headless Bundle&lt;/a> for more details.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>List</title><link>https://kaiiiz.github.io/hugo-theme-monochrome/layouts/docs/list/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kaiiiz.github.io/hugo-theme-monochrome/layouts/docs/list/</guid><description>&lt;p>List layout is built-in section layout. Monochrome add options to adjust its behavior.&lt;/p>
